;   Version 9.5, 15-OCT-2023, DD: Updated for FRA_MODE=2 (i.e., PCA background subtraction)
;   Version 9.6, 04-SEP-2024, DD: Added FRA_MODE=3 (mean) and FRA_MODE=4 (median). FRA_MODE=0 is now legacy
